title: Tuesday Post Show (08-09-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (08-09-22)
description:
Bobby starts talking about some of the behind the scenes of his new show Snake in the Grass. Why science says your parents dictate the quality of your marriage, Ashton Kutcher revealed a rare disease he battled recently and the Top 25 college team football rankings. Bobby revealed he got invited on a really cool podcast that he’s excited about. We also review a clip of Eddie’s recent reel and the weird voice he used recording it.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
